spirit:busInterface.spirit:name: S_AXI
spirit:busInterface.spirit:description: s_axi bus interface that supports both AXI4 and AXI4Lite

spirit:modelParameter.spirit:name: C_INCLUDE_GLOBAL_BUFFERS
spirit:modelParameter.spirit:displayName: Include global buffers for PHY clocks

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_RX_PING_PONG
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Set this parameter to include the no. of Receive Buffers.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_TX_PING_PONG
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Set this parameter to include the no. of Transmit Buffers.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_INCLUDE_GLOBAL_BUFFERS
spirit:parameter.spirit:displayName: Enable Global Buffers for PHY Clocks
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Enabling this parameter includes global buffers for PHY clocks which can be used to minimize the clock skew on the PHY clocks.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_INCLUDE_INTERNAL_LOOPBACK
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Enabling this parameter includes BUFG for PHY clock switching when loopback is enabled.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_INCLUDE_MDIO
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Including the MDIO interface allows PHY register access from AXI Ethernet Lite MAC core.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_S_AXI_PROTOCOL
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: This parameter decides the AXI interface of the core.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_DUPLEX
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Set this parameter for choosing Full Duplex or Half Duplex mode.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: AXI_ACLK_FREQ_MHZ
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: The AXI4 clock frequency must be greater than or equal to 100 MHz for 100 Mb/s Ethernet operation and greater than or equal to 10 MHz for 10 Mb/s Ethernet operation.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: Enable_Constraints
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Enabling this parameter includes I/O constraints on the PHY ports through TCL. If internal PHY is used, this parameter has to be disabled.
